Subject: [PATCH] Use system libraries

---
 CMakeLists.txt                | 85 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---
 core/archive/7zArchive.cpp    |  7 +++
 core/archive/7zArchive.h      |  5 +++
 core/archive/archive.cpp      |  4 ++
 core/rend/vulkan/compiler.cpp |  4 ++
 core/rend/vulkan/shaders.h    |  4 ++
